data.description: Spacious 4 bed, 3 bath home in Lagrange, Georgia, meticulously maintained since its construction in 2020. This recently built beauty boasts modern amenities and style throughout. Every detail has been thoughtfully crafted, offering a turnkey living experience. All major systems have been recently serviced, ensuring peace of mind for the lucky new owner. Step outside to a fully fenced backyard, providing privacy and space for outdoor enjoyment. Located in a desirable area, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Don't miss your chance to own this pristine property - schedule a showing today!
